Four suspects were arrested and two firearms recovered on Saturday morning. The Nelspruit Flying Squad received a report of a vehicle hijacking in Mbombela . The vehicle was spotted and a high speed chase ensued towards KaNyamazane. Suspects shot at the flying squad members from the fleeing vehicle and the police returned fire.
The vehicle was forced to a stop at the entrance to KaNyamazane and suspects jumped out and start running away. All four suspects were arrested. The police are still searching for the other firearms.